text: Kamianske () is a city in the Dnipropetrovsk Oblast (province) in Ukraine. It is the administrative centre of Kamianske Raion (district). In 2024, 240,000 people lived there. It is an important industrial city. From 1936 to 2016, the city was known as Dniprodzerzhynsk. Population: == References == == Other websites == * Category:Cities in Dnipropetrovsk Oblast
